    <description>(ADG&amp;rsquo;s Description:)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mech in Flames (MiF) a 200 counter sheet expansion for World in Flames that adds engineers, mech and motorized corps, garrison units supply and forts to spice up your next game of World In Flames.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A World in Flames Expansion.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mech In Flames includes engineers, supply units, and fortresses, and some late-war corps for various powers that appeared earlier in other expansions such as Leaders in Flames (LIF). It introduces some new &amp;quot;city-based volunteer&amp;quot; corps (mostly militia) for the US, Commonwealth, France, and Japan. It has a smattering of new naval and air units. It has a garrison unit for Portugal that will make a common British strategy of attacking Portugal in 1939 more difficult. And it updates the Soviet Guard Banner Armies introduced first in LIF.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Part of World in Flames 1994/95 Annual which is a &amp;quot;72 page Annual including tips, hints and after action replays of World in Flames, Days of Decision II, Ships in Flames and Planes in Flames&amp;quot;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
